FBIS4-36158 "drnes109_j_94011" FBIS-NES-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Aden Radio Reports Successes of Southern Forces Aden Radio Reports Successes of Southern Forces Destroyed Vehicles Listed EA0606162094 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1400 GMT 6 Jun 94 EA0606162094 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1400 GMT 6 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Text] We have received the following from the Defense Ministry: Our forces have repulsed desperate and aggressive assaults mounted by the forces of the ruling military regime in Sanaa on various fronts. Our Armed Forces dealt crushing blows against the enemy forces in the following areas: On the Abyan axis they destroyed eight tanks and three (Daskas), and captured five tanks. On the Tawr al-Bahah/Khara axis they destroyed eight tanks and three (Daska) vehicles, and captured four tanks. Meanwhile, our forces are continuing, with rare courage, to repulse the forces of aggression on all fronts. God is great. God is great.
